  "content": "ing long I/O</div>\n    <div style=\"color: var(--text-secondary); padding-left: 24px;\">Old index deallocation blocks tokio runtime</div>\n    <div style=\"color: var(--text-secondary); padding-left: 24px;\">No swap event logged for observability</div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-red);\">2</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Critical</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-amber);\">2</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Important</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-blue);\">3</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Low</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p>Both criticals were real bugs. Without this review, queries would have hit a half-built index during rebuilds. All 7 findings were fixed in a single commit.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">06 / 09</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SLIDE 7: THE NUMBERS -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">The Numbers</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    1 in 8 Commits Is<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-amber\">a Review Fix</